feedback_entries.post_content: Evolving Skies at $150 is decent considering the Eeveelution Alt Arts inside! Just know the pull rates can be brutal 🤩 #HighRiskHighReward
feedback_entries.feedback: DO NOT include hashtags when replying to tweets. This would be a hard one because the evolving skies set is at over $1800 now, so commenting the wrong thing about price can trigger a lack of understanding on our side. If you have data on the prices from TCG player in real time, you can check and see that this would be a steal and it might mean it's too good to be true. The comment about pull rates is great.

feedback_entries.post_content: ETBs give you dice, sleeves, and storage box, but boosters have better value per pack. Depends if you want the extras or maximum pack opening! ⚡️
feedback_entries.feedback: Good, you can also claim that people tend to keep ETBs sealed and they tend to rise in price over time. Also, pokemon center ETBs are always more sought after. ETBs usually come with a promo card as well.

feedback_entries.post_content: Start with a Trainer Kit or Battle Academy! Great for learning the game, then move to theme decks or an Elite Trainer Box for their favorite set 😍
